Dear Giuseppe, dear all,=0A=
=0A=
I am shocked to learn that Bob Walters is gone.=0A=
I knew him from the time I visited Max Kelly in Australia.=0A=
He was a very friendly person with a good sense of humor.=0A=
And a good mathematician too.=0A=
He was an adventurer, both in math and in life.=0A=
The last time I saw him was at the CT2010 meeting in Genova.=0A=
I am using his work with Carboni and Kasangian in my latest paper=0A=
with Gambino.=0A=
=0A=
My deepest condoleance to his friends and family,=0A=
Andr=E9=0A=
=0A=
